column5: Will...hope you have a great birthday!  Since I didn't get you a gift or anything, I figured my gift for you would be to let everyone here know....and maybe they'll get you something.    I made this for you, but I got hungry and ate it...sorry
Happy Birthday, Will!!!  Hope you are having a "crappie" day!!!!
Happy Birthday Will....have an awesome day !
Happy B-Day you ole bugger! HH
Yep... hope you're having a good day you old bugger!
All the best to ya Will, have a great Birthday !!
Happy Birthday Will, hope you have a great day

Thanks for the birthday wishes.  Had a great day, slept in, a bite to eat and on the water at the crack of noon. (I could get use to that.) It was a great day on the lake, never caught so many bluegills before. A few perch and the WGSF were willing to bite as well. Found a nice school of crappie and brought a few home for dinner. The rain held off too! It was an awesome way to spend the day.
Well a day late and a dollar short but I'll share a drink with you soon young man.
same here, with luck this Sat. over some Road Gravy...
